  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Safety and efficacy of antibiotic steroid combination compared with individual administration
      in the treatment of bacterial ocular inflammation and infection (blepharitis and/or keratitis
      and/or conjunctivitis).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Antibiotic/steroid combination compared to individuals components 8 days of treatment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
